trans-unit.source: Provides a mechanism for routing the workflow instance ID to and from a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowWebService"></xref> to a cookie in the Web client.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller en mekanism för routning av arbetsflödesinstans-ID till och från en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowWebService"> </xref> till en cookie i webbklienten.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This functionality is required to reenter a workflow definition that is exposed as a Web service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Den här funktionen krävs för att ange en arbetsflödesdefinition som visas som en webbtjänst.

trans-unit.source: Without this module, the first call to the workflow-exposed Web service works, but subsequent calls fail.
trans-unit.target: Det första anropet till webbtjänsten arbetsflödet exponeras fungerar utan den här modulen, men efterföljande anrop misslyckas.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, make sure that the client application has cookies enabled.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollera dessutom att klientprogrammet har cookies är aktiverade.

trans-unit.target: Släpper de resurser som används av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A> when you are finished using the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>.
trans-unit.target: När <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A>du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A> method leaves the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> in an unusable state.

After calling <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> occupied.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A>, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>upptaget.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule.System.Web.IHttpModule.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Annars frigörs inte resurser den använder tills skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowWebHostingModule>
